{"tid":452590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日發生既事太美好","createTime":"2017-10-30T11:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T12:47:17.000Z","uid":137088,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ffec96700edff1d043d6c4140c32f2ab2ae9b113","tid":452590,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"多年前睇過&quot;哈佛大學幸褔課&quot;呢本書,睇完就忘記左佢,今日先知錯過左寶,入面既智慧千金難買,今日開始努力每日實行,下面分享我今日既感恩既事。<br />\n<br />\n三件感恩的事<br />\n1. 發現我以前睇野太封閉,好似井底之蛙咁,今日先發現世界係咁美好<br />\n2. 多謝爸爸為我煮既午飯,媽鎷煮既晚飯,佢地日日默默咁為我付出,我以前居然視若無睹,爸爸媽媽我愛你<br />\n3. 感謝以往日子曾幫助我既人<br />\n<br />\n日行一善<br />\n1. 係抑鬱POST度盡力答左幾個有疑惑既人,希望佢地有所得益"},{"pid":"bc12af73e99a422906ad542cb4d83dbc20d37cfd","tid":452590,"uid":15984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:14:02.000Z","msg":"好，連登仔港獨之後，比個社工大都督你做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccef2c2d499b8b7bd102a2eef11e40d044290356","tid":452590,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:21:20.000Z","msg":"搭巴士都要記得感恩"},{"pid":"ac15a6098802d1a6dfab6025084dce9f9b4de88d","tid":452590,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:23:49.000Z","msg":"五毛版:<br />\n<br />\n1) 感謝黨中央<br />\n2) 感謝雜種大大<br />\n3) 感謝幹部的任命<br />\n<br />\nloop x 365"},{"pid":"cc710c0dd3bbed690b6aaf03ad1a8f531835cef9","tid":452590,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭巴士都要記得感恩</blockquote><br />\n抄低左,聽日有內容可以寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37bf2e95230709b5e6c103b08934ba842ea55df","tid":452590,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}